gṛdhrādibhir vipralujyamāna itastataḥ pratikāram ātmarakṣaṇārthaṃ kim iti na karotīti pṛcchati sarvasāmarthyavikalatvāt. ata eva cittaparikarmaiva sādhyam. tasmin parikarmite kāyasyāyatnata eva parikarmasiddheḥ, tatparatantratvāt tasyety uktaṃ bhavati.

<commentary>evaṃ sarvathānupayogini kāye sāpekṣatāṃ nirasyann āha.

he manaḥ, anātmakam eva ātmatvena svīkṛtya māṃsāsthipuñjaṃ kāyasaṃjñakaṃ kasmāt kāraṇāt tvaṃ rakṣasi? kim evam iti cet, bhavato yadi bhinna evāyaṃ kāyaḥ. tena asyāpacaye tava kim apacīyate?</commentary>

pūrvam eva ciraṃ svīkṛta iti ced āha. he mūḍha, mohavijṛmbhitam etad bhavataḥ. śuciṃ pavitram.